16. Persons liable to pay value added tax.—Every person specified below
shall be liable to pay VAT‚ namely—
(a) in relation to taxable import: the importer;
(b) in relation to any taxable supply in Bangladesh: the supplier;
(c) in relation to any taxable supply of imported service: the recipient of
such supply;
(d) in relation to any sale, in the prescribed manner, of any good by an
auctioneer on behalf of a registered person: the auctioneer.
